# 🤖 Concierge — AI Omnichannel Support Agent (WIP)

> 🚧 Building in public. An AI customer-support agent with human handoff:
> answers from a knowledge base and escalates to a human when it can't resolve.

## The idea
Ingest real support conversations → knowledge base (Postgres + pgvector) →
an AI agent answers on the channel (chat first, then voice and email) and
**hands off to a human** when confidence is low.

## Planned stack
PostgreSQL + pgvector · Python (FastAPI) · LLM + RAG · Whisper + Asterisk (voice) ·
Docker · GitHub Actions (CI/CD) · Terraform · GCP (Cloud Run) · Prometheus/Grafana · GKE

## Roadmap
- [x] Repo + scaffold
- [ ] M0 — local docker-compose (Postgres + pgvector + service + chat + RAG + handoff)
- [ ] M1 — CI/CD pipeline
- [ ] M2 — IaC + deploy to GCP
- [ ] M3 — observability

